headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid PNC and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: PNC Financial Services Group has been treading water for the past six months, recording a small loss of 4.7% while holding steady at $191.55. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 5.4% gain during that period.
